{
  "stem": "23090.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, it was still wonderful, under all these terrible conditions and under all these-- situation-- under the situation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was still with my mother, and we still were a family unit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to a child, that is the most wonderful, protective, warm, indescribable feeling-- is to be with your parents under any conditions, virtually any conditions.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't care if you have to share a rat's tail to-- for food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It is the love of your mother who hugs you and the nice words and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So in a way, under even those microscopic conditions, it was still a good condition, because I was still in my family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were still a unit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as the war progressed, and as we continued in the ghetto, the Germans virtually built a whole government, a government of, of, of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] like you read, it was the Master Plan.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They, they enlisted and incorporated our own people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They built a police force.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They built two police forces, some of a higher order, some of a lower order, that I lived with, that I saw, that I was part of.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the scare tactics now began from the inside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you were rewarded if you did something for the Germans from the inside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So if [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you wanted to inform on somebody you didn't like, then you went to the [GERMAN], or you went to a Jewish policeman, or you went to someone that has contact with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And you said Sam Kellman has got a lot of gold, which I know he has been stashing for the last 10, 15, 20 years.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was the whole crux for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
